name: SpacePhoto
0:
”Alexa, open Space Photo”
”Alexa, ask Space Photo for today's photo”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: space photo
des: 'Space Photo' provides a brief explanation of what today's Astronomy Photo of the Day is. A longer summary as well as the photo can be found within the Alexa App as well as on the Echo Show Display.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
